name: YELP
description: Yelp is a platform that provides user-generated reviews and ratings for businesses, particularly restaurants."

name: DATA SCIENCE REPORT
description: A report investigating the success of different cuisines in various cities using Yelp data."

name: CHINESE CUISINE
description: A type of cuisine that includes dishes originating from China, analyzed in the report."

name: ITALIAN CUISINE
description: A type of cuisine that includes dishes originating from Italy, noted for its popularity in the report."

name: PIZZA CUISINE
description: A type of cuisine characterized by its pizza dishes, included in the analysis of restaurant success."

name: LAS VEGAS
description: A city noted for having a high number of reviews for restaurants, particularly Italian cuisine."

name: SCOTTSDALE
description: A city that also shows a trend of higher review counts for restaurants, regardless of cuisine."

name: ONE-WAY ANOVA TEST
description: A statistical test used to determine significant differences in review counts among different cuisines across cities."

name: LOGISTIC REGRESSION MODEL
description: A predictive model used to classify restaurant success based on ratings, achieving 83% accuracy."

name: AUC (Area Under Curve)
description: A measure indicating the performance of the logistic regression model, noted to be 0.5, suggesting no predictive power."

name: BOX PLOTS
description: A graphical representation used to illustrate the distribution of ratings for different cuisines across cities."

name: REVIEW COUNT
description: The number of reviews received by restaurants, a key metric in the analysis."

name: SUCCESS RATE
description: The percentage of restaurants with ratings above a certain threshold, used to define success in the report."

name: RATING THRESHOLD (3.5 STARS)
description: The minimum rating used to classify a restaurant as successful in the logistic regression model."

name: TOP 10 CITIES
description: The ten cities with the highest number of reviews, selected for detailed analysis in the report."

name: TOURISTS
description: Visitors who may influence the number of reviews and restaurant success in cities like Las Vegas."
